{
  "stem": "15686.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't know where I belonged.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And now I was supposed to study English and go to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So-- but the first thing was to get a job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So somehow through some friends, I don't know, I got a job to work in a bakery in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this little bakery was owned by a German Jewish couple who had been here for many years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They emigrated back in the 20s, but they were-- they spoke-- spoke German, so I could communicate with them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I worked from 7:30 in the morning until 6 o'clock in the afternoon, six days a week, for $8 a week.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was the prevailing wage at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is 1941, now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had been working for about a month when Pearl Harbor Day arrived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the United States was at war with Japan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now, of course, there was absolutely no hope of getting any news whatsoever from my parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My grandparents, who had been in the-- in New York, in the Bronx, and my uncle and aunt had had some news from my parents.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had received some letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while life was very tough for them, they had survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But all communication stopped again on December 7th, 1941.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to work, as I said, during the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after work, I went to high school at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I didn't know enough English to get into college.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I did a full high school program in two years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I graduated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was valedictorian of my class.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went to evening high school in the Bronx and took a full academic course.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
